    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed or flagged under Minimal profile conformance. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification demonstrates hemolysis predictions below clinical threshold at 3 of 5 operating conditions. Residual gaps in model form, test conditions, and equivalency of input parameters are acknowledged. Package accepted under Minimal profile with documented epistemic gaps pending resolution in subsequent assessment cycle.",
